        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer990667761" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12088532483405685332"><i>Preface<br/>A Note on Japanese Names and Dates<br/>Introduction (Cultural Background, The Author, The Diary)</i><br/><br/>--The Diary of Lady Murasaki<br/><br/><i>Appendix 1: Ground-plans and Map<br/>Appendix 2: Additional Sources<br/>A Guide to Further Reading</i></span>

          </span>
        </div>


