        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3674482576" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15952974828200867090">At first I thought it was lovely as Murasaki included poems and descriptions of her surroundings. Still over time it dragged on. She wrote of the petty details of court life. She said she was not interested in such things, and over time I was not either. </span>

          </span>
