        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4019023105" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer236186012507936147">I didn&apos;t enjoy this nearly as much as <i>Bridge of Dreams</i>, since this one is far less dreamy and delicate and more quotidian, but I guess Murasaki gets a pass for writing <i>The Tale of Genji</i> and generally being a genius. Still, it&apos;s always amazing to read 1000-year old diaries, even if they are 80% gossip.</span>
  <span id="freeText236186012507936147" style="display:none">I didn't enjoy this nearly as much as <i>Bridge of Dreams</i>, since this one is far less dreamy and delicate and more quotidian, but I guess Murasaki gets a pass for writing <i>The Tale of Genji</i> and generally being a genius. Still, it's always amazing to read 1000-year old diaries, even if they are 80% gossip.</span>
